title: Sercos
description: OPC 30100: Mapping of Sercos services and objects (IDNs) to OPC UA so that a vendor independent access to information provided by Sercos devices is given. Sercos devices are controls, drives, I/Os and other decentralized peripheral, such as encoders, safety devices and vision systems.
